{"tid":1710355,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港中文大學關於校園安全的聲明","createTime":"2019-11-12T07:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:32:59.000Z","uid":268836,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4d024a25cbcc85ab2e9ddca16f736508ebc82420","tid":1710355,"uid":268836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"【香港中文大學關於校園安全的聲明(11月12日)】<br />\n<br />\n今天(11月12日)早上大約10:30左右，有人破壞夏鼎基運動場的門鎖，擅自闖入器材倉庫，並取走一批用於體育運動用途的弓、箭、標槍等物資。由於箭頭由金屬造成，如果不當使用，對四周途人將會構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n校方代表迅速處理事件，已經取回已知被取走的所有物品。<br />\n<br />\n校方亦呼籲校內學生、職員，在校園出入時必須遠離發生衝突的地點，以免發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n無言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推學生去死，不要信校方談判呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcbfdec